Multi-user drawing app.

Features:

* Multiplayer drawing.
* Colour picker
* Chat
* Drawing stays in server memory and is transmitted when user joins.

License: MIT
Author: Tim Sullivan <tim@timatooth.com>

Credit: tutorialzine for initial code.

# Installation & Setup


Install and run Redis: http://redis.io/download

    redis-server

Run the application via node:

    cd node-multidraw
    npm install
    node server.js

To run it daemonised, use `forever`, `daemonize2` or this command form:

    cd node-multidraw; nohup node server.js >/dev/null 2>&1 &

# Usage

Once running visit

`localhost:5000` for default canvas: "main lobby"

or

`localhost:5000/c/room-name` to create a new canvas

